  "texts": [
    "Thus, the miss rates for B_L are negligible but at the cost of the lowest accuracy.",
    "B_H is the worst in terms of inference throughput and bandwidth requirement (26Mbps).",
    "Hence, B_H has the highest miss rate for almost all settings.",
    "B_M has better performance than other baselines but fails to provide consistency like Jellyfish does for all settings.",
    "B_M has high miss rates in the following two cases: (a) Low SLOs and low request rates: Clients need around 7Mbps to send frames at the desired size (354 × 354) and 15 FPS."
